Task 2 of 1

4) If you decide to share 4 points with your partner, and he decided to share half of what he received, how many points would you end up with in this round?

a) 16

b) 0

c) 9

Correct!

The correct response is c).

If you share 4 out of 5 points with your partner and he decided to share half with you, you would receive 8 points back (i.e. (4 x 4)/2 = 8), totaling to 9 points altogether.
